Package: TfuncViz
Title: T Cell Functionality Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person( "Zhan" , "2974249021@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analyzing and visualizing T cell functionality scores from single-cell RNA-seq data. 
    Includes PCA-based visualization, heatmaps, and comparison plots between disease and healthy conditions.
